GetGoingFast ComfyUI L2P Z-Image

This project packages a ComfyUI custom node wrapper and workflow for the
L2P Z-Image 6B pixel-space model.

The vendored `diffsynth` runtime files are adapted from the public Hugging Face
Space `multimodalart/z-image-6b-pixel-space`, which is published under the
Apache-2.0 license and uses the L2P model from `zhen-nan/L2P`.

Links:
